Package: trendDataETL
Title: Process and Analyze Music Streaming Platform Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Cesaire", "Tobias", email = "ces@precise.digital", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package to process, standardize, and analyze music streaming data 
    from different Digital Service Providers (DSPs). It connects to Google Drive,
    retrieves files, standardizes formats, and stores data in a SQL database for
    historical trend analysis across platforms like Spotify, Apple Music, and others.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
